@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cazfwi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.15 / v2 + 0.77)))
    v0 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.69 + v1 + 0.98)) + ((v1 + 0.77 * v0 + 0.76) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.92)))
    v1 = (0.48 - (0.34 * (v0 + 0.87 - tmp + 0.05)))
    tmp = ((0.29 / (v0 + 0.59 * v2 + 0.53)) / v2)
    data[tid] = v0
